08</a>.</p><p><a href=\"https://datasets.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/be.vl.omgeving.erkenningen.distribution.opleidingscentra_technici_brandbeveiligingsapparatuur.pdf\">Download the list of recognised training centres for fire protection equipment technicians here.</a></p><p>Those who pass the exam receive a <strong>European certificate</strong> (certificate of competence). The training institute also registers your certificate in the Database of Qualifications and Professional Experience Attestations (LED) of the Flemish government.</p><p><strong>STEP 2: </strong><a href=\"https://loket-erkenningen-leefmilieu.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/registreer-voor-erkenning-van-rechtswege\">Register for recognition as a fire protection equipment technician via the self-management counter 'My VLAREL recognition'</a>.</p><ul><li>You need to register with your eID at the counter. Without registration, you cannot start working as a fire protection equipment technician. </li><li>As soon as you have obtained a <strong>European certificate </strong>and <strong>registered </strong>, you will receive an <strong>e-mail with your recognition number</strong> and further info.</li></ul><h3><strong>You already have a European certificate as a fire protection equipment technician </strong></h3><p><strong>STEP 1: </strong><a href=\"https://loket-erkenningen-leefmilieu.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/registreer-voor-erkenning-van-rechtswege\">Register for recognition as a fire protection equipment technician via the self-management counter 'My VLAREL recognition'.</a></p><p><strong>STEP 2: </strong>Provide a copy of <strong>your European certificate</strong> in Dutch, French, German or English via <strong>a notification of the use of a recognition</strong> in the <a href=\"https://www.uat-vlaanderen.be/natuur-milieu-en-klimaat/erkenning-als-technicus-deskundige-opleidingscentrum-of-labo/erkenningenloket-omgeving\" data-story-block-title=\"Online Erkenningenloket Omgeving\" data-story-block-identifier=\"fb9ee7a6-